4ï¸âƒ£ elif (else if)

Used when there are multiple conditions.

marks = int(input("Enter marks: "))

if marks >= 90:
    print("Grade A")
elif marks >= 75:
    print("Grade B")
elif marks >= 50:
    print("Grade C")
else:
    print("Fail")

5ï¸âƒ£ Comparison Operators (Very Important)
